{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":880,"text":"\"Mom, who are these people?\""},{"time":3480,"text":"It was an innocent question\nfrom my young daughter Alia"},{"time":6120,"text":"around the time when she was three."},{"time":8280,"text":"We were walking along with my husband"},{"time":10400,"text":"in one of Abu Dhabi's big fancy malls."},{"time":13200,"text":"Alia was peering at a huge poster\nstanding tall in the middle of the mall."},{"time":17520,"text":"It featured the three rulers\nof the United Arab Emirates."},{"time":21760,"text":"As she tucked in my side,"},{"time":23240,"text":"I bent down and explained\nthat these were the rulers of the UAE"},{"time":26480,"text":"who had worked hard\nto develop their nation"},{"time":28760,"text":"and preserve its unity."},{"time":31040,"text":"She asked, \"Mom, why is it\nthat here where we live,"},{"time":34920,"text":"and back in Lebanon,\nwhere grandma and grandpa live,"},{"time":37600,"text":"we never see the pictures\nof powerful women on the walls?"},{"time":40760,"text":"Is it because women are not important?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":44040,"text":"This is probably the hardest question\nI've had to answer in my years as a parent"},{"time":47880,"text":"and in my 16-plus years\nof professional life, for that matter."},{"time":52120,"text":"I had grown up in my hometown in Lebanon,"},{"time":55120,"text":"the younger of two daughters\nto a very hard-working pilot"},{"time":58600,"text":"and director of operations\nfor the Lebanese Airlines"},{"time":62240,"text":"and a super-supportive\nstay-at-home mom and grandma."},{"time":65960,"text":"My father had encouraged\nmy sister and I to pursue our education"},{"time":70080,"text":"even though our culture\nemphasized at the time"},{"time":73400,"text":"that it was sons and not daughters\nwho should be professionally motivated."},{"time":78840,"text":"I was one of very few girls\nof my generation"},{"time":81040,"text":"who left home at 18 to study abroad."},{"time":84480,"text":"My father didn't have a son,"},{"time":86320,"text":"and so I, in a sense, became his."}]},{"cues":[{"time":90880,"text":"Fast-forward a couple of decades,\nand I hope I didn't do too badly"},{"time":94600,"text":"in making my father proud\nof his would-be son."},{"time":98680,"text":"As I got my Bachelor's and PhD\nin electrical engineering,"},{"time":101840,"text":"did R&amp;D in the UK,\nthen consulting in the Middle East,"},{"time":105360,"text":"I have always been\nin male-dominated environments."},{"time":108720,"text":"Truth be told, I have never found\na role model I could truly identify with."},{"time":114240,"text":"My mother's generation\nwasn't into professional leadership."},{"time":117880,"text":"There were some\nencouraging men along the way,"},{"time":120080,"text":"but none knew the demands\nand pressures I was facing,"},{"time":124000,"text":"pressures that got particularly acute\nwhen I had my own two beautiful children."},{"time":129759,"text":"And although Western women love to give us\npoor, oppressed Arab women advice,"},{"time":135160,"text":"they live different lives\nwith different constraints."}]},{"cues":[{"time":139120,"text":"So Arab women of my generation\nhave had to become our own role models."},{"time":143240,"text":"We have had to juggle more than Arab men,"},{"time":145520,"text":"and we have had to face\nmore cultural rigidity than Western women."},{"time":149720,"text":"As a result, I would like to think\nthat we poor, oppressed women"},{"time":153840,"text":"actually have some useful,\ncertainly hard-earned lessons to share,"},{"time":158000,"text":"lessons that might turn out useful"},{"time":160040,"text":"for anyone wishing to thrive\nin the modern world."},{"time":163440,"text":"Here are three of mine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":164760,"text":"[\"Convert their sh*t into your fuel.\"]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":166640,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":167880,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":174280,"text":"There is this word that everybody\nis touting as the key to success:"},{"time":178680,"text":"resilience."},{"time":180520,"text":"Well, what exactly is resilience,\nand how do you develop it?"},{"time":184640,"text":"I believe resilience is simply\nthe ability to transform shit into fuel."}]},{"cues":[{"time":191640,"text":"In my previous job,\nwell before my current firm,"},{"time":194480,"text":"I was working with a man\nwe will call John."},{"time":197400,"text":"I had teamed up with John\nand was working hard,"},{"time":199840,"text":"hoping he would notice how great I was"},{"time":201840,"text":"and that he would come to support\nmy case to make partner at the firm."},{"time":206040,"text":"I was, in addition to delivering\non my consulting projects,"},{"time":209240,"text":"writing passionately on the topic\nof women economic empowerment."},{"time":213880,"text":"One day, I got to present my research\nto a roomful of MBA students."},{"time":218560,"text":"John was part of the audience"},{"time":220160,"text":"listening for the first time\nto the details of my study."},{"time":224000,"text":"As I proceeded with my presentation,"},{"time":226320,"text":"I could see John in the corner of my eye."},{"time":229000,"text":"He had turned a dark shade of pink"},{"time":231560,"text":"and had slid under his chair\nin apparent shame."}]},{"cues":[{"time":235840,"text":"I finished my presentation\nto an applauding audience"},{"time":238320,"text":"and we rushed out and jumped into the car."},{"time":241480,"text":"There he exploded."},{"time":244040,"text":"\"What you did up there was unacceptable!"},{"time":246240,"text":"You are a consultant, not an activist!\""},{"time":249600,"text":"I said, \"John, I don't understand."},{"time":252080,"text":"I presented a couple of\ngender parity indices,"},{"time":255760,"text":"and some conclusions about the Arab world."},{"time":257839,"text":"Yes, we do happen to be today\nat the bottom of the index,"},{"time":260839,"text":"but what is it that I said or presented\nthat was not factual?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":265040,"text":"To which he replied,\n\"The whole premise of your study is wrong."},{"time":269120,"text":"What you are doing is dangerous and will\nbreak the social fabric of our society.\""},{"time":273720,"text":"He paused, then added,"},{"time":276120,"text":"\"When women have children,\ntheir place is in the home.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":281360,"text":"Time stood still for a long while,"},{"time":283640,"text":"and all I could think and repeat\nin the chaos of my brain was:"},{"time":287360,"text":"\"You can forget about\nthat partnership, Leila."},{"time":289560,"text":"It's just never going to happen.\""},{"time":292680,"text":"It took me a couple of days to fully\nabsorb this incident and its implications,"},{"time":296600,"text":"but once I did,\nI reached three conclusions."},{"time":300160,"text":"One, that these were his issues,"},{"time":302720,"text":"his complexes."},{"time":304240,"text":"There may be many like him in our society,"},{"time":306320,"text":"but I would never let\ntheir issues become mine."},{"time":309400,"text":"Two, that I needed\nanother sponsor, and fast."}]},{"cues":[{"time":312360,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":313600,"text":"I got one, by the way,\nand boy, was he great."},{"time":315840,"text":"And three, that I would get to show John\nwhat women with children can do."},{"time":320280,"text":"I apply this lesson equally well\nto my personal life."},{"time":323720,"text":"As I have progressed in my career,"},{"time":325520,"text":"I have received many words\nof encouragement,"},{"time":328000,"text":"but I have also often been met\nby women, men and couples"},{"time":332320,"text":"who have clearly had an issue\nwith my husband and I"},{"time":335080,"text":"having chosen the path\nof a dual-career couple."}]},{"cues":[{"time":338600,"text":"So you get this well-meaning couple"},{"time":340720,"text":"who tells you straight out\nat a family gathering"},{"time":343000,"text":"or at a friends gathering,"},{"time":344280,"text":"that, come on, you must know\nyou're not a great mom,"},{"time":346733,"text":"given how much you're investing\nin your career, right?"},{"time":350720,"text":"I would lie if I said\nthese words didn't hurt."},{"time":353440,"text":"My children are the most\nprecious thing to me,"},{"time":355920,"text":"and the thought that I could be\nfailing them in any way is intolerable."},{"time":360480,"text":"But just like I did with John,"},{"time":362040,"text":"I quickly reminded myself\nthat these were their issues,"},{"time":365680,"text":"their complexes."},{"time":367520,"text":"So instead of replying,"},{"time":368840,"text":"I gave back one of my largest smiles"},{"time":371160,"text":"as I saw, in flashing light,"},{"time":373040,"text":"the following sign in my mind's eye."}]},{"cues":[{"time":375200,"text":"[Be happy, it drives people crazy.]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":377280,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":382760,"text":"You see, as a young woman\nin these situations, you have two options."},{"time":386120,"text":"You can either decide\nto internalize these negative messages"},{"time":389000,"text":"that are being thrown at you,"},{"time":390640,"text":"to let them make you feel like a failure,"},{"time":392640,"text":"like success is way too hard\nto ever achieve,"},{"time":395240,"text":"or you can choose to see that others'\nnegativity is their own issue,"},{"time":398680,"text":"and instead transform it\ninto your own personal fuel."},{"time":402880,"text":"I have learned\nto always go for option two,"},{"time":406080,"text":"and I have found that it has taken me\nfrom strength to strength."},{"time":409800,"text":"And it's true what they say:"},{"time":411280,"text":"success is the best revenge."}]},{"cues":[{"time":414960,"text":"Some women in the Middle East"},{"time":416400,"text":"are lucky enough to be married\nto someone supportive of their career."},{"time":419840,"text":"Correction: I should say \"smart enough,\""},{"time":422320,"text":"because who you marry is your own choice,"},{"time":424720,"text":"and you'd better marry someone supportive\nif you plan to have a long career."},{"time":429240,"text":"Still today, the Arab man\nis not an equal contributor in the home."},{"time":433560,"text":"It's simply not expected by our society,"},{"time":435800,"text":"and even frowned upon as not very manly."},{"time":439360,"text":"As for the Arab woman,\nour society still assumes"},{"time":442080,"text":"that her primary source of happiness\nshould be the happiness and prosperity"},{"time":445840,"text":"of her children and husband."},{"time":447800,"text":"She mostly exists for her family."},{"time":451160,"text":"Things are changing,\nbut it will take time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":453760,"text":"For now, it means\nthat the professional Arab woman"},{"time":456280,"text":"has to somehow maintain the perfect home,"},{"time":459640,"text":"make sure that her children's every need\nis being taken care of"},{"time":462760,"text":"and manage her demanding career."},{"time":465760,"text":"To achieve this, I have found the hard way"},{"time":469120,"text":"that you need to apply your hard-earned\nprofessional skills to your personal life."},{"time":473920,"text":"You need to work your life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":476000,"text":"Here is how I do this in my personal life."},{"time":480998,"text":"One thing to know about the Middle East"},{"time":482880,"text":"is that nearly every family\nhas access to affordable domestic help."},{"time":487320,"text":"The challenge therefore becomes\nhow to recruit effectively."},{"time":491160,"text":"Just like I would in my business life,\nI have based the selection"},{"time":494480,"text":"of who would support me\nwith my children while I'm at work"},{"time":497560,"text":"on a strong referral."},{"time":499280,"text":"Cristina had worked\nfor four years with my sister"},{"time":502240,"text":"and the quality of her work\nwas well-established."},{"time":505880,"text":"She is now an integral\nmember of our family,"},{"time":508160,"text":"having been with us\nsince Alia was six months old."},{"time":511400,"text":"She makes sure that the house\nis running smoothly while I'm at work,"},{"time":514919,"text":"and I make sure to empower her"},{"time":517159,"text":"in the most optimal conditions\nfor her and my children,"},{"time":520360,"text":"just like I would my best talent at work."},{"time":523559,"text":"This lesson applies\nwhatever your childcare situation,"},{"time":527160,"text":"whether an au pair, nursery,"},{"time":529600,"text":"part-time nanny\nthat you share with someone else."},{"time":531960,"text":"Choose very carefully, and empower."}]},{"cues":[{"time":536040,"text":"If you look at my calendar,"},{"time":537400,"text":"you will see every working day"},{"time":539400,"text":"one and a half hours\nfrom 7pm to 8:30pm UAE time"},{"time":543120,"text":"blocked and called \"family time.\""},{"time":545800,"text":"This is sacred time."},{"time":547360,"text":"I have done this\never since Alia was a baby."},{"time":551040,"text":"I do everything in my power\nto protect this time"},{"time":553480,"text":"so that I can be home by then\nto spend quality time with my children,"},{"time":556920,"text":"asking them about their day,"},{"time":559360,"text":"checking up on homework,\nreading them a bedtime story"},{"time":562280,"text":"and giving them\nlots of kisses and cuddles."},{"time":564880,"text":"If I'm traveling,\nin whatever the time zone,"},{"time":567400,"text":"I use Skype to connect with my children\neven if I am miles away."},{"time":572200,"text":"Our son Burhan is five years old,"},{"time":574280,"text":"and he's learning to read\nand do basic maths."}]},{"cues":[{"time":577920,"text":"Here's another confession:"},{"time":579520,"text":"I have found that our daughter\nis actually more successful"},{"time":582280,"text":"at teaching him these skills than I am."}]},{"cues":[{"time":584200,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":586800,"text":"It started as a game, but Alia loves\nplaying teacher to her little brother,"},{"time":590880,"text":"and I have found that these sessions\nactually improve Burhan's literacy,"},{"time":596080,"text":"increase Alia's sense of responsibility,"},{"time":598480,"text":"and strengthen the bonding between them,"},{"time":600480,"text":"a win-win all around."}]},{"cues":[{"time":603520,"text":"The successful Arab women I know"},{"time":605760,"text":"have each found their unique approach\nto working their life"},{"time":608920,"text":"as they continue to shoulder"},{"time":610320,"text":"the lion's share\nof responsibility in the home."}]},{"cues":[{"time":613040,"text":"But this is not just\nabout surviving in your dual role"},{"time":615680,"text":"as a career woman and mother."},{"time":617400,"text":"This is also about being in the present."},{"time":621000,"text":"When I am with my children,"},{"time":622880,"text":"I try to leave work out of our lives."},{"time":625320,"text":"Instead of worrying about how many minutes\nI can spend with them every day,"},{"time":629360,"text":"I focus on turning these minutes\ninto memorable moments,"},{"time":633160,"text":"moments where I'm seeing my kids,"},{"time":635400,"text":"hearing them, connecting with them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":637240,"text":"[\"Join forces, don't compete.\"]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":639040,"text":"Arab women of my generation\nhave not been very visible"},{"time":641840,"text":"in the public eye as they grew up."},{"time":643960,"text":"This explains, I think, to some extent,"},{"time":645880,"text":"why you find so few women\nin politics in the Arab world."},{"time":649320,"text":"The upside of this, however,"},{"time":650840,"text":"is that we have spent a lot of time"},{"time":652960,"text":"developing a social skill\nbehind the scenes,"},{"time":657040,"text":"in coffee shops, in living rooms,"},{"time":658840,"text":"on the phone,"},{"time":660080,"text":"a social skill that is\nvery important to success:"},{"time":662880,"text":"networking."},{"time":664560,"text":"I would say the average Arab woman"},{"time":666240,"text":"has a large network\nof friends and acquaintances."},{"time":668800,"text":"The majority of those are also women."}]},{"cues":[{"time":672400,"text":"In the West, it seems like ambitious women\noften compare themselves to other women"},{"time":676400,"text":"hoping to be noticed as the most\nsuccessful woman in the room."},{"time":680360,"text":"This leads to the much-spoken-about\ncompetitive behavior"},{"time":683160,"text":"between professional women."},{"time":685560,"text":"If there's only room\nfor one woman at the top,"},{"time":687760,"text":"then you can't make room for others,\nmuch less lift them up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":691760,"text":"Arab women, generally speaking,"},{"time":693280,"text":"have not fallen\nfor this psychological trap."},{"time":696280,"text":"Faced with a patriarchal society,"},{"time":698240,"text":"they have found\nthat by helping each other out,"},{"time":700600,"text":"all benefit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":703120,"text":"In my previous job, I was the most\nsenior woman in the Middle East,"},{"time":706320,"text":"so one could think that investing\nin my network of female colleagues"},{"time":710200,"text":"couldn't bring many benefits"},{"time":711800,"text":"and that I should instead invest my time"},{"time":714080,"text":"developing my relationships\nwith male seniors and peers."},{"time":717760,"text":"Yet two of my biggest breaks\ncame through the support of other women."},{"time":722200,"text":"It was the head of marketing\nwho initially suggested"},{"time":724680,"text":"I be considered as a young global leader\nto the World Economic Forum."},{"time":728000,"text":"She was familiar with my media engagements\nand my publications,"},{"time":731000,"text":"and when she was asked\nto voice her opinion,"},{"time":733120,"text":"she highlighted my name."},{"time":735280,"text":"It was a young consultant,\na Saudi lady and friend,"},{"time":737960,"text":"who helped me sell\nmy first project in Saudi Arabia,"},{"time":740720,"text":"a market I was finding hard\nto gain traction in as a woman."},{"time":744840,"text":"She introduced me to a client,"},{"time":746360,"text":"and that introduction led to the first\nof very many projects for me in Saudi."},{"time":750520,"text":"Today, I have two senior women on my team,"},{"time":753000,"text":"and I see making them successful\nas key to my own success."},{"time":758320,"text":"Women continue to advance in the world,"},{"time":760320,"text":"not fast enough, but we're moving."}]},{"cues":[{"time":762720,"text":"The Arab world, too, is making progress,\ndespite many recent setbacks."},{"time":766840,"text":"Just this year, the UAE appointed\nfive new female ministers to its cabinet,"},{"time":771480,"text":"for a total of eight female ministers."},{"time":774360,"text":"That's nearly 28 percent of the cabinet,"},{"time":777080,"text":"and more than many\ndeveloped countries can claim."},{"time":779920,"text":"This is today my daughter\nAlia's favorite picture."},{"time":783360,"text":"This is the result,\nno doubt, of great leadership,"},{"time":785880,"text":"but it is also the result\nof strong Arab women"},{"time":788520,"text":"not giving up and continuously\npushing the boundaries."},{"time":791520,"text":"It is the result of Arab women\ndeciding every day like me"},{"time":795680,"text":"to convert shit into fuel,"},{"time":797480,"text":"to work their life\nto keep work out of their life,"},{"time":800040,"text":"and to join forces and not compete."}]},{"cues":[{"time":802960,"text":"As I look to the future,"},{"time":804400,"text":"my hopes for my daughter\nwhen she stands on this stage"},{"time":806960,"text":"some 20, 30 years from now"},{"time":808800,"text":"are that she be as proud\nto call herself her mother's daughter"},{"time":811920,"text":"as her father's daughter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":814040,"text":"My hopes for my son"},{"time":815520,"text":"are that by then, the expression\n\"her mother's son\" or \"mama's boy\""},{"time":819160,"text":"would have taken on\na completely different meaning."}]},{"cues":[{"time":822120,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":823360,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}